FBIS3-55937 "drsov008_b_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Directive on Cadre Policy Council Task PM1101133394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA in Russian 11 Jan 94 p 5 PM1101133394 Moscow ROSSIYSKAYA GAZETA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Directive No. 792-rp of the Russian Federation President, signed by Russian Federation President B. Yeltsin, dated 31 December 1993] [Text] In accordance with the Statute on the Council for Cadre Policy Under the President of the Russian Federation, ratified by edict No. 848 of the president of the Russian Federation dated 3 June 1993: 1. The Council for Cadre Policy Under the President of the Russian Federation is charged with overal coordination of the work to prepare draft acts of the president of the Russian Federation, whose adoption is necessitated by the Statute on the Federal State Service, ratified by edict No. 2267 of the president of the Russian Federation dated 22 December 1993. 2. V.F. Shumeyko and S.A. Filatov, cochairmen of the Council for Cadre Policy Under the President of the Russian Federation, are to submit for ratification within 10 days a work schedule for the preparation of draft acts indicated in Point 1 of this directive. [Signed] President of the Russian Federation B. Yeltsin [Dated] 31 December 1993
